org.apache.hadoop.yarn.server.api.records

Class OpportunisticContainersStatus

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.yarn.server.api.records.OpportunisticContainersStatus
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    OpportunisticContainersStatusPBImpl

    @InterfaceAudience.Private
@InterfaceStability.Unstable
public abstract class OpportunisticContainersStatus
extends Object

    OpportunisticContainersStatus captures information pertaining to the state of execution of the opportunistic containers within a node.
